content:
Opening of schools 101

State schools opening, as many parents of those kids need to work for billionaires who fund the Tories

Private schools stay closed, can afford remote learning, plus most of the parents outsource their kids anyway or think the risk is too high

content:
During the work-from-home period I got into the habit of exercising daily (instead of commuting.) I lost about 8kg (~18lbs).

Now that I‚Äôm back at work it‚Äôs harder to exercise and the weight is slowly starting to come back.

Trying to fight against it.

Now someone comes along:

For those working from home for the first time: ensure you google ‚Äòbest practices‚Äô, and there are many!
